---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - FishLog" description="FishLog Terms of Service. Read our terms and conditions for using the app.">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Last Updated: January 2025</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          By downloading, installing, or using FishLog, you agree to these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use the app.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. Use of the App</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">You agree to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Use the app only for personal, non-commercial purposes</li>
          <li>Provide accurate information when creating an account</li>
          <li>Keep your account credentials secure</li>
          <li>Comply with all applicable fishing laws and regulations</li>
          <li>Not use the app for any illegal or unauthorized purpose</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. AI Features Disclaimer</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          FishLog's AI species identification and measurement features are provided for informational purposes only. While we strive for accuracy, AI predictions may contain errors. Always verify species identification and comply with local fishing regulations. We are not responsible for decisions made based on AI predictions.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. User Content</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          You retain ownership of photos and data you upload. By using FishLog, you grant us a license to store, process, and display your content to provide our services. You are responsible for ensuring you have rights to any content you upload.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Subscriptions & Payments</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Pro subscriptions are billed through the App Store. Subscriptions auto-renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Manage subscriptions in your device settings.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          FishLog is provided "as is" without warranties. We are not liable for any damages arising from your use of the app, including but not limited to lost data, fishing violations, or decisions based on AI features.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">7. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the app after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">8. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Questions about these terms? Contact us at:
          <a href="mailto:legal@fishlog.app" class="text-ocean-blue hover:underline">legal@fishlog.app</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
